  "texts": [
    "We also observe (figures in Supplementary Section C) that the surrogate recreates the rich spatial patterns of predator-prey clusters, also seen in similar settings in evolutionary game theory [27].Quantitative results.",
    "Now we present the results of a quantitative analysis, systematizing the previous comparisons.",
    "Here, each comparison with the ground truth is quantified using one of the metrics presented in the previous subsection, i.e.",
    "Earth Mover's Distance (EMD) for the microlevel comparisons, and sMAPE for the macro-level ones.",
    "Figure 4 summarizes the results of our experiments: the left panel shows the microscopic evaluation of both our surrogate model and the ablated variant, while the right panel presents the macroscopic evaluation results.For the Schelling model, we observe that, on the micro level, the surrogate's mean EMD is lower than the diffusion-only ablation's mean EMD in all cases."
  ]
